title: Farming/Level up table
content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Farming/Level up table
LevelNew abilities
Each level
  • Completing difficulties of the Kandarin Diary grants a higher yield of herbs by 5%/10%/15% for the medium, hard, and elite difficulties respectively for the Catherby herb patch
  • Completing the Hard Kourend & Kebos Diary increases the yield from crops in the Farming Guild and Hosidius patches
  • Herb patches will have a 5% greater yield while wearing the farming cape
  • The magic secateurs grants a 10% increase in yield of crops when wielded and higher quality herbs from the Herbiboar
